Package humandeque.manager

Class CollectionManager

java.lang.Object
humandeque.manager.CollectionManager
Direct Known Subclasses:
LocalManager
public abstract class CollectionManager extends Object
An abstract class for managing a collection of Human objects. This class provides common manipulations for a HumanDeque collection, including adding, updating, and removing elements from the collection. It also allows the collection to be loaded and saved from a storage medium using a CollectionStorage object.
